  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a study intended to evaluate the efficacy and safety of the vibrating capsule versus
      sham non-vibrating capsule on spontaneous bowel movement, in aiding reliving Constipated
      Individuals
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
