  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Frequency of bowel movements</measure>
    <time_frame>3 months</time_frame>
    <description>change from baseline in the weekly Spontaneous Bowel Movement (SBM) rate during treatment period. Success will be defined as increase by at least 1 SBM/week. The primary analysis will be a comparative analysis of success rates between the study groups</description>
  </primary_outcome>
